name: Katanaes Zambon
description:
An enhance version of Katanaes Shinzon Zambon is now a General Class Soldier whose purpose is to guide the interplanetary adventurers their purpose is help from civilzation to civilization. She is an overpowered support non-combat class type you can rely on.

She was constructed by The Shinzon Family when she is struck by the bullet from her head.

This Bio-Android of her is more advance than any other Bio-Android made by Shinzon Family.

Constructed date year 2030
